WEBVTT

00:00:14.065 --> 00:00:16.718
What is at the center of the universe?

00:00:16.742 --> 00:00:18.054
It's an essential question

00:00:18.078 --> 00:00:21.140
that humans have
been wondering about for centuries.

00:00:21.164 --> 00:00:22.947
But the journey toward an answer

00:00:22.971 --> 00:00:24.406
has been a strange one.

00:00:24.430 --> 00:00:26.764
If you wanted to know
the answer to this question

00:00:26.788 --> 00:00:28.850
in third century B.C.E. Greece,

00:00:28.874 --> 00:00:30.494
you might look up at the night sky